name: PD Games Vol. 226
overview: A public domain release from The Assassins that contained Jumping Jack, Technoball and Zillo. These compilations were sold by mail order through a number of suppliers of public domain software who would usually assign their own catalogue number, so it is not uncommon to find the same compilation on offer from multiple suppliers in the same magazine, usually for a fairly nominal fee above the cost of the disk and copying labor.
